description.en: Floki One is the first Floki on the Harmony Mainnet, having launched on September 12th, 2021. Each transaction is subject to a 8% tax, with 4% going towards liquidity and the remaining 4% getting redistributed amongst holders. Floki is more than just a meme coin, as it is launching its own NFT line, an NFT Marketplace, as well as two play-to-earn games.
